author: SleeplesSSP
title: Okay. Just okay.
review:
Actually not very good for displaying the CMF series, the 4x4 plates are just loosely slid into each thing rather than attached and some larger CMF characters and characters with too many props won't fit unless you really force them to.

Looks great when you finally manage to get them in, though. I love this item outside the obvious design flaws.
